</bo--><div id="column-center"><h3>WARRANTY &amp; RETURN POLICY</h3><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"></span> </p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">Make an order from thehermeshandbags.com you should agree with our policy.<br />If you have problems with your product or are unsatisfied with your order, we will refund or exchange your product within 10 days of delivery.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong>Important:</strong><br />Some rare models may be out of stock on the moment of purchase, so we'll notify you if it happens after purchase. We'll ask you to choose another model which is very close to </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">the original or fully refund your payment.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong>Delivery is guaranteed</strong><br />We will reship again at our expense if your package is lost or seized.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong>10-Days Unconditional Satisfaction Guarantee</strong><br />If you are not satisfied with your product in anyway, you may return it within 10 days for a full refund or exchange. We understand how important it is for you to verify all </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">products ordered meet your expectations. For we absolutely guarantee you receive the exact same products as seen on our website.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong>Manufacturer’s warranty</strong><br />Hermes quality products: 6 months. Warranty covers all manufacturers’ defects on all different parts of the product. </span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong>Returns</strong><br />Please send us an email at stating the problem. Let us know whether it is a refund, exchange, or repair under the manufacturer’s warranty. We need your order number, and </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">approximate purchase date. We will send you the address where you should send the product you want refunded, exchanged or repaired. Once the product is received, and the </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">product has not been worn or tampered with; a full refund will be made to you, or a new product will be shipped to you.</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">Here are the details you need to state:<br />1. Your order number<br />2. Product(s) you want to return<br />3. The reason you want to make a return.<br />4. Tracking numbers after your product has been sent out</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><em><font color="#ff0000"><strong>If you are returning products for exchange / refund</strong></font></em><br />  1. The product condition must be 100% BRAND NEW - this means never worn nor unpacked. This also means that the plastic wrapping around the band of the products must </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">be intact and not removed<br />  2. Please insure your return. We are not responsible for lost or damaged products during the shipping process. All shipping costs incurred as such are not refundable. The </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">product is subject to final inspection for the above conditions before your return is processed<br />  3. You are responsible for shipping costs back to us. If price of the exchanged product is higher than original purchase, please enclose a payment for the price difference. If </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">the price of the exchanged product is lower, we will issue a refund for the difference in price.<br />  4. Tampered products will not be exchanged / refunded. This means that if the products have been opened up, or otherwise tampered or damaged, the return / refund policy </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">will be considered null and void<br />  5. In case of package being lost, there is a 30- day waiting period before refund. This allows us to track and place a claim on package.<br />  6. If you return an order that was placed using a promotional certificate or discount, you will not be refunded for the amount of the promotional offer, as these discounts were </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">deducted from the original purchase amount. Any unexpired promotional funds used on the order would, however, be returned to your account for use toward future qualifying </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">purchases. Please note that the original expiration date still applies</span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US"><strong><em><font color="#ff0000">If you are returning products for warranty</font></em></strong><br />  1. Only manufacturer’s defects are covered under warranty. This does not include intentional damage, or general wear and tear (such as scratches, dents etc).<br />  2. Make sure the crown is always screwed in tight to prevent water from penetrating. If we detect any damage caused by the crown not being tight, we are not likely to cover </span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">the damage.<br />  3. If any of the products have been tampered with, the warranty is void.<br />  4. If a manufacturer’s defect appears on the product within 1 week of ordering, we will replace it with a brand new one.<br />  5. If your product cannot be repaired, we will send you a replacement of the exact same model. If that model is out of stock, then you can choose another product of the </span></p><p><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; FONT-SIZE: 10pt" lang="EN-US">same or lesser value. In most cases, we repair the products having manufacturers' defects.</span></p></div><br class="clear" />